item.title: Golden Gate Bridge
item.description: Must-see views of the bridge You canâ€™t visit San Francisco without visiting the Golden Gate Bridge! I’ll share a few must see angles and their map pin in this post. The Golden Gate Overlook This is a great spot to checkout the bridge. It is seldom crowded and ample free/paid parking spots can be found close by.
